\par \pard \widctlpar Ldp is a utility for testing LDAP client APIs for Windows NT. Ldp\rquote s functionality provides an interface that can be used for limited browsing and administration. Since it was written to test Microsoft\rquote s wldap
32.dll LDAP library, it is API oriented. That is, Ldp\rquote s user interface maps directly to LDAP v.2 API set. Similarly, Ldp\rquote 
s output indicates what functions were called and what were the results. Hence, familiarity with LDAP API specifications is highly recommended.
\par \pard \widctlpar 
